description: ELECTION OF SPEAKER OF HOUSE OF REPRESENTATIVES, F. WOOD (DEM.), VERSUS J.G. BALINE (REP.).  MINOR CANDIDATES WERE H. CLYMER (DEM., PENNSYLVANIA), S.S. COX (DEM., NEW YORK), AND A.H. STEPHENS, (DEM., GEORGIA).  VOTES FOR WOOD ARE CODED AS 1, FOR BLAINE, S 2, FOR CLYMER, AS 5, FOR COX, AS 6, AND FOR STEPHENS, AS 7.
